  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BE A CAT and SAVE YOUR HUMAN from the GREEBLES!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Itty Bitty Toilet Kitty</i>, you play as a cute feline on a mission to protect your beloved human from flesh-eating toilet monsters — the dreaded <strong>GREEBLES</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What to expect:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A microgame — around <strong>15 minutes</strong> of total playtime</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A very silly story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple but fun gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A retro-style soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >My first solo dev project</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CAT!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Note from the developer:</strong><br>I made this game after losing my job as a games writer. Originally, it was a paid game (99p) — after being unemployed for a year and a half, I couldn’t justify not charging something.<br>Now that I’m back working as a games writer again, I’ve decided to make it <strong>free forever</strong>.<br>It’s a very silly little game, but it brought me a lot of joy during a dark time, and I hope it brings a smile (and maybe a laugh) to anyone who gives it a try.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/c0d58ca76570bfca95dc0b4c0eedf1b8.poster.avif?t=1762882358\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/c0d58ca76570bfca95dc0b4c0eedf1b8.webm?t=1762882358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/c0d58ca76570bfca95dc0b4c0eedf1b8.mp4?t=1762882358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/ced29341db06dfd3b9d8a297790af76b.poster.avif?t=1762882358\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/ced29341db06dfd3b9d8a297790af76b.webm?t=1762882358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/ced29341db06dfd3b9d8a297790af76b.mp4?t=1762882358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/7aa3bf4d36360d29c834bde402c81bce.poster.avif?t=1762882358\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/7aa3bf4d36360d29c834bde402c81bce.webm?t=1762882358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/7aa3bf4d36360d29c834bde402c81bce.mp4?t=1762882358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/6e193be8d49115c4f44948675949c9c8.poster.avif?t=1762882358\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/6e193be8d49115c4f44948675949c9c8.webm?t=1762882358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/6e193be8d49115c4f44948675949c9c8.mp4?t=1762882358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BE A CAT and SAVE YOUR HUMAN from the GREEBLES!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Itty Bitty Toilet Kitty</i>, you play as a cute feline on a mission to protect your beloved human from flesh-eating toilet monsters — the dreaded <strong>GREEBLES</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What to expect:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A microgame — around <strong>15 minutes</strong> of total playtime</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A very silly story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple but fun gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A retro-style soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >My first solo dev project</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CAT!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Note from the developer:</strong><br>I made this game after losing my job as a games writer. Originally, it was a paid game (99p) — after being unemployed for a year and a half, I couldn’t justify not charging something.<br>Now that I’m back working as a games writer again, I’ve decided to make it <strong>free forever</strong>.<br>It’s a very silly little game, but it brought me a lot of joy during a dark time, and I hope it brings a smile (and maybe a laugh) to anyone who gives it a try.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/c0d58ca76570bfca95dc0b4c0eedf1b8.poster.avif?t=1762882358\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/c0d58ca76570bfca95dc0b4c0eedf1b8.webm?t=1762882358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/c0d58ca76570bfca95dc0b4c0eedf1b8.mp4?t=1762882358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/ced29341db06dfd3b9d8a297790af76b.poster.avif?t=1762882358\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/ced29341db06dfd3b9d8a297790af76b.webm?t=1762882358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/ced29341db06dfd3b9d8a297790af76b.mp4?t=1762882358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/7aa3bf4d36360d29c834bde402c81bce.poster.avif?t=1762882358\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/7aa3bf4d36360d29c834bde402c81bce.webm?t=1762882358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/7aa3bf4d36360d29c834bde402c81bce.mp4?t=1762882358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/6e193be8d49115c4f44948675949c9c8.poster.avif?t=1762882358\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extras/6e193be8d49115c4f44948675949c9c8.webm?t=1762882358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049450/extra